data.description: ***MOTIVATED SELLER***RECENT UPGRADES! TURN KEY HOME!!!! Discover the comfort and style in this 3 bed 3 bath residence with a spacious loft in a guard gated community.  With a well-designed layout, this home is complete with lush greenery , manicured yard and scenic privacy. BEDROOM DOWNSTAIRS! An open floor plan with plenty of natural light in a community where you can escape from the hustle and bustle of city life! A TON OF UPGRADES including plantation shutters, quartz countertops, Solar, osmosis water filtration, vinyl flooring and MORE!  Balcony off primary to relax and unwind. Los Prados offers golf, trails, restaurant, pool, RV parking, tennis courts & MORE!!! This home isn’t just a property, it’s a lifestyle waiting for you. Come and experience it for yourself.
